   <S PAR='54' RSNT='1' SNO='54'>of the Believers at the Judgment Seat of Christ</S>
   <S PAR='55' RSNT='1' SNO='55'>and in the Coming Kingdom</S>
   <S PAR='56' RSNT='1' SNO='56'>19.</S>
   <S PAR='57' RSNT='1' SNO='57'>Concerning the Kingdom, Millennium,</S>
   <S PAR='58' RSNT='1' SNO='58'>and the Age of Restoration</S>
   <S PAR='59' RSNT='1' SNO='59'>The kingdom is the millennium, and the millennium of one thousand years is the age of restoration.</S>
